OL,6,F"This will clearly have a significant
OL,7,Fimpact on our operation and our
OL,8,Fcustomers, and we're working as
OL,9,Fquickly as possible to update them on
OL,10,Ftheir travel options for the next 24
OL,11,Fhours and beyond."
OL,13,FThe Government will be doing
OL,14,Feverything it can to restore power to
OL,15,FHeathrow Airport, Energy Secretary Ed
OL,16,FMiliband has said.
