OL,3,CHow long will the Heathrow Airport
OL,4,Cdisruption last and what are my rights?
OL,6,F"The government is hard at work,
OL,7,Fmyself and my colleagues, are doing
OL,8,Feverything we can to help both
OL,9,FHeathrow and the National Grid," Mr
OL,10,FMiliband said.
OL,12,F"I think the important thing for now
OL,13,Fis to get power restored...that is the
OL,14,Fabsolute priority," he added.
OL,16,FConsultant John Strickland warned that
OL,17,Fflight disruption from the closure of
OL,18,FHeathrow could be expected to run for
OL,19,F"several days".
