OL,3,CHow long will the Heathrow Airport
OL,4,Cdisruption last and what are my rights?
OL,6,FHe told PA: "With nothing possible in
OL,7,Fand out of the airport today, that's a
OL,8,Fmassive dislocation to have to recover
OL,9,Ffrom.
OL,11,F"We're talking about several days
OL,12,Fworth of disruption to get the planes
OL,13,Frecovered and start using them again
OL,14,Fto move planned and disrupted
OL,15,Fpassengers."
OL,17,FTravel expert Simon Calder said the
OL,18,Fdisruption at Heathrow will be off the
OL,19,Fscale, with Friday the busiest day of
OL,20,Fthe week at the busiest airport in
OL,21,FEurope.
