OL,3,CHow long will the Heathrow Airport
OL,4,Cdisruption last and what are my rights?
OL,6,F"British Airways is going to have its
OL,7,Fplanes, its passengers, its pilots in
OL,8,Fall the wrong places, and until that
OL,9,Fgets sorted out, people are going to
OL,10,Fbe flummoxed," he said.
OL,12,F"Even if we are lucky enough to get
OL,13,Fthings back on track, and the pictures
OL,14,Fwe've been seeing of the fire suggest
OL,15,Fthat's not going to happen anytime
OL,16,Fsoon, then immediately they can start
OL,17,Fto rebuild the operation, but it's
OL,18,Fgoing to take days," he added.
