OL,3,CHow long will the Heathrow Airport
OL,4,Cdisruption last and what are my rights?
OL,6,FUnder UK law, those affected by flight
OL,7,Fdelays or cancellations have legal
OL,8,Frights which oblige airlines to
OL,9,Fprovide support to customers flying
OL,10,Ffrom a UK airport, arriving in the
OL,11,Fcountry on a European Union (EU) or UK
OL,12,Fairline, or arriving at an EU airport
OL,13,Fon a UK airline.
OL,15,F"If you're booked on British Airways,
OL,16,For any other airline from Heathrow
OL,17,Ftoday, then the airline has to get you
OL,18,Fto your destination as soon as
OL,19,Fpossible," Simon Calder said.
