OL,3,CHow long will the Heathrow Airport
OL,4,Cdisruption last and what are my rights?
OL,6,FIf your flight is covered under UK
OL,7,Flaw, your airline must give you the
OL,8,Foption of choosing another flight or
OL,9,Fproviding a full refund. You can get
OL,10,Fmoney back on any part of the ticket
OL,11,Fnot used.
OL,13,FIf you still want to travel, your
OL,14,Fairline must find you an alternative
OL,15,Fflight. If another airline is flying
OL,16,Fto your destination significantly
OL,17,Fsooner, or there are other suitable
OL,18,Fmodes of transport available, then you
OL,19,Fhave a right to be booked onto that
OL,20,Falternative transport instead.
