OL,3,CHow long will the Heathrow Airport
OL,4,Cdisruption last and what are my rights?
OL,6,FCauses of disruption classed as
OL,7,Foutside their control include severe
OL,8,Fweather, air traffic control
OL,9,Frestrictions and security alerts.
OL,11,FIn this case, Rory Boland said: "If
OL,12,Fyour flight is cancelled you won't be
OL,13,Fentitled to compensation as these
OL,14,Fevents will be considered an
OL,15,Fextraordinary circumstance but you
OL,16,Fwill be entitled to assistance from
OL,17,Fyour airline, including overnight
OL,18,Faccommodation if needed."
